  "content": "### \ud83d\udcc1 Claude Folder Directory Architecture and Guidelines\n\n<div className=\"flex justify-center my-6\">\n  <img src=\"/assets/digest/6.jpeg\" className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-xl max-w-full h-auto mx-auto\" alt=\"Claude Folder Architecture\" />\n</div>\n\nA detailed companion guide to structuring your local workspace directories. Learn how to optimize paths, establish boundaries, and write high-fidelity brief files.\n\n---\n\n### \ud83d\udccc Folder Best Practices\n\n- **ABOUT ME Folder:** Store your profile and voice guides. Let Claude know your specific coding styles, formatting preferences, and forbidden words.\n- **TEMPLATES Folder:** Save successful structures (like API templates, component boilerplates) for Claude to copy.\n- **CLAUDE OUTPUTS:** Make sure this is the only folder Claude has write permissions to. This protects your source reference files from accidental overwriting."
