  "content": "### \ud83d\ude80 20 Ways to Leverage Claude in Your Daily Workflow\n\n<div className=\"flex justify-center my-6\">\n  <img src=\"/assets/digest/8.jpeg\" className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-xl max-w-full h-auto mx-auto\" alt=\"20 Ways to use Claude\" />\n</div>\n\nExplore 20 distinct use cases for Claude, from rendering artifacts, chat sessions, using Opus 4.8's deep thinking mode, and setting custom prompt constraints for multi-file editing.\n\n---\n\n### \ud83d\udca1 Productivity Blueprints\n\n- **Render Artifacts:** Use Claude's rendering capabilities to preview React components, vector diagrams, and flowcharts in real time.\n- **Deep Thinking Mode:** Toggle Opus's reasoning capabilities for debugging complex concurrency bugs or architectural design patterns.\n- **Code Refinement:** Feed Claude target snippets with specific instructions to refactor and optimize performance."
